pve-lxc-syscalld (2.0.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * replace dedicated lazy_static crate with LazyLock from std lib.

  * service: avoid using generic runtime directory name, as when the service
    is restarted, the directory will be recreated, which can have dire
    consequences for other daemons reusing this generic directory.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Thu, 31 Jul 2025 01:28:12 +0200

